abstract: >
A production-ready prompt injection detection framework for LangChain,
providing multi-layer defense through regex-based patterns, heuristic scoring,
and optional machine learning classification. The system includes evaluation
pipelines for synthetic, real-world, and adversarial datasets, along with
middleware integration for agentic AI systems.

